biblScope\">20</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"b\" id=\"n56825.1\" level=\"4\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> esp. of the fox, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0232.tlg001:89:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Archil.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">89.5</biblScope> </bibl>: hence <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἡ κ.</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">the wily one, the fox</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0545.tlg001:6:64\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Ael.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ NA\">NA</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.64</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; cf. <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">κερδώ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0545.tlg001:1\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n56825.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> of things, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">profitable</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0033.tlg002.perseus-grc1:2:78\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pi.\">Pi.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ P.\">P.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.78</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg002.perseus-grc1:3:4:11\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Mem.\">Mem.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.4.11</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">κερδαλεώτερόν ἐστι ὁμολογέειν τῷ Πέρσῃ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:9:7\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"bibl